> Depth Charge jumped to the side holding his blade so Thrasher could not go
> after them.
>

{Thrash}

    Thrash regarded the bot blocking his path, these two more aggressive
bots seemingly forgetting the third his eyes eying the blad and shrugged
hopping up transforming into a floating giant white shark, its maw opening
impossibly wide revealing the barrel of a drunk missile launcher in the
creatures throat area, his voice seemed unhampered as he spoke, "The names
Thrash, Predicon brute squad, and while I don't give a slag about the
escaping bot yer pathetic attempt to threaten me with yer tooth pick is much
more interesting."

    The barrel of the drunk missile launcher slowly started to rotate as if
preparing to fire on the bot, "Now stand down before I slag yer skid
plate...First and only request."
